    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "It would be helpful to have a way to silently send messages to the message history. For example, you could use this to display an on-screen error message and follow it with a backtrace (or some other useful context) sent silently to message history so when the user runs `:messages` they see the error with the context but when they are notified that an error happened they just see the main error text without noise.",
    "closed_at": "2023-04-13T06:34:37Z",
