            "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
            "body": "Is requesting features from vim and then waiting for a patch a requirement? Per https://github.com/neovim/neovim/issues/2514#issuecomment-580135150, I thought this wasn't needed. I think Neovim feature development would be unlocked somewhat if it could implement features independently and let Vim pull them in after the fact instead of only pulling from Vim.",
