        {
            "author_association": "MEMBER",
            "body": "I don't think this is the way we want to address the underlying issue here; the goal is rather to enrich our Neovim API for messages with metadata so users can despatch them however they wish, see https://github.com/neovim/neovim/issues/22478 (which I'm closing this one as duplicate of, since it should cover this use case as well.)\r\n\r\n(And I kinda agree with Bram here: `:message` history is not a log file, and we should not confuse the two.)",
